name: Delaney H Mathews
bio: When Delaney H. Mathews was born on 10 July 1858, in Brooks, Covington, Alabama, United States, her father, John L Mathews, was 33 and her mother, Ellafair, was 40. She had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with William Beauregard Bennett. She lived in Covington, Alabama, United States in 1860 and Red Level, Covington, Alabama, United States in 1900. She died on 21 March 1901, at the age of 42.
